Important

Scam update - 28 June:

We have been made aware of a scam related to Telstra bonds, where the ASX-listed bonds issued by XTB are used as a point of reference.

Please do not provide your personal or financial information on comparison investments websites or over the phone. If you have been a victim of this scam, please call us on 133464. For more information, visit: https://asic.gov.au/about-asic/news-centre/news-items/warning-telstra-bonds-investment-opportunities-are-fake/

SCAM ALERT

Fraudsters and scammers are currently attempting to exploit people's concerns about coronavirus (COVID-19) through phishing campaigns.

For more information on these scams and how to protect yourself, visit https://www.staysmartonline.gov.au/alert-service/widespread-reports-covid-19-malicious-scams-being-sent-australians.
